    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
    </p>
    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
     NOTICE:
    </p>
    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
     <span style="font-weight: 400">
      This sign can mean such 
    things as "catch my eye" or "I picked that one out right away."
